After MQ client installation We need to copy  the Client Channel Definition Table from MQ server(C:\ProgramData\IBM\MQ\qmgrs\TFMQM\@ipcc\AMQCLCHL.TAB) to client side   (var/mqm/AMQCLCHL.TAB) if it is not done u can perform below steps to 
unset ccdt checking.
 
 
unset MQCHLLIB
unset MQCHLTAB
env | egrep MQCHL
export MQSERVER="CIMPLR.TO.SAA.SVRCON/TCP/10.24.219.48(1416)"
cd /opt/mqm/samp/bin/
./amqsputc CIMPLR.TO.SAA TFMQM
